# Changelog

2017-01-13 New release, v0.1.2
    FIXES
    - segment fault when updating gui inside mplayer thread (after system update)
    FEATURES
    - new default conf radios

2014-12-03 New release, v0.1.1
    FIXES
    - fixed text color in the gtk dialog for the dark theme
    - fixed a new error which occurs when double clicking the station icon
    FEATURES
    - added icon
    - added support for window resizing

2013-11-22 First stable release, v0.1.0
